## all 'alt' can be replaced to 'command' in mac env.

Contrl short-cut of keyboard
ctrl + p ==  cmmand palette
	-- 1. first u can type in string like 'javascript' to choose adopting javascript syntax
	-- 2. 

ctrl + tab/shift-tab == change the file we already opened
	-- just like switch tab in Chrome browser

ctrl + p == open files in ur folder/project

shift + F11 == change to the full-screen mode of editing
	-- the view of this mode can be setting by opening
		1. Preferences --> settings-More --> Distraction 
		2. the above will open file named : Distraction Free.sublime-settings
		3. type : 
			{
 		   		"line_numbers": true,      //是否顯示行號
    			"gutter": false,   //文件左邊是否顯示裝訂邊
    			"draw_centered": true,      //是否置中顯示
    			"wrap_width": 140,          //每一行顯示的寬度(以字元計算)
    			"word_wrap": true,         //是否自動換行
    			"scroll_past_end": false  //Scroll Bar的顯示是否超過文件的結尾
			}

ctrl + shift + M == 選取對應括號內的多行文字(ex: {},[])

ctrl + j == 合併多行成一行

ctrl + d == 選取輸入點所在文字 
	-- 連續按 可以選取  

ctrl + l == 選取多行
	-- 再用 ctrl + shift + 上/下  : 可以移動整排

ctrl + r == finding function tha already be definde in ur doc

ctrl + g == finding the line number u would like to locate

ctrl + ` == open the python command window

ctrl + shift + / == 多行注釋


Package related : 
1. package control : 
		-- open python command window by ctrl + `
		-- paste : import urllib2,os; pf='Package Control.sublime-package'; ipp=sublime.installed_packages_path(); os.makedirs(ipp) if not os.path.exists(ipp) else None; urllib2.install_opener(urllib2.build_opener(urllib2.ProxyHandler())); open(os.path.join(ipp,pf),'wb').write(urllib2.urlopen('http://sublime.wbond.net/'+pf.replace(' ','%20')).read()); print 'Please restart Sublime Text to finish installation'
		-- restart sublime text2

With the installation of 'package control',We can manage/install packages by it

2. Themr package: 
	-- open command palette
	-- input 'install package'
	-- input 'Themr'

3. Soda-theme package: 
	-- open command palette
	-- input 'install package'
	-- input 'Theme Soda'

4. IMESupport package(中文字輸入支援): 
	-- open command palette
	-- input 'install package'
	-- input 'IMESupport'

5. Alignment package(程式碼對齊)":
	-- open command palette
	-- input 'install package'
	-- input 'Alignment'
	-- restart sublime text2
	usage : 
		-- select several lines of code 
				-- ctrl + L 
		-- ctrl + alt + a
